---
// OfferCard - Seção com detalhes da oferta de recuperação
---

<section class="offer-section" id="oferta">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-badge">Oferta Especial</span>
      <h2>Uma oferta pensada para você voltar</h2>
      <p>Condições exclusivas por tempo limitado para retomar seus estudos de inglês</p>
    </div>

    <div class="offer-grid">
      <div class="offer-card reveal">
        <div class="offer-card-header">
          <span class="offer-tag">Plano Recuperação</span>
          <div class="offer-price-block">
            <span class="currency">R$</span>
            <span class="price">140</span>
            <span class="period">/mês</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="offer-card-body">
          <div class="offer-breakdown">
            <div class="breakdown-item">
              <div class="breakdown-icon points">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                  <path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="breakdown-info">
                <span class="breakdown-value">300 pontos</span>
                <span class="breakdown-label">= 6 aulas/mês</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="breakdown-plus">+</div>

            <div class="breakdown-item bonus">
              <div class="breakdown-icon tickets">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M20 12v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6"/>
                  <path d="M4 8V6a2 2 0 012-2h12a2 2 0 012 2v2"/>
                  <rect x="2" y="8" width="20" height="4" rx="1"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="breakdown-info">
                <span class="breakdown-value">24 tickets/mês</span>
                <span class="breakdown-label">nos 3 primeiros meses</span>
                <span class="breakdown-detail">Para professores de 5, 25 ou 40 pts</span>
                <span class="breakdown-bonus">Bônus grátis!</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="offer-total">
            <div class="total-line">
              <span class="total-label">Total nos 3 primeiros meses</span>
              <span class="total-value">até 30 aulas/mês</span>
            </div>
            <div class="total-line">
              <span class="total-label">Após 3 meses</span>
              <span class="total-value">6 aulas/mês (300 pts)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="total-line highlight">
              <span class="total-label">Preço por aula (3 meses)</span>
              <span class="total-value">R$ 4,67</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <ul class="offer-features">
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/>
              </svg>
              Aulas de 25 minutos ao vivo
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/>
              </svg>
              Professores certificados TESOL
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/>
              </svg>
              Disponível 24h, 7 dias por semana
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/>
              </svg>
              Cancele quando quiser
            </li>
          </ul>

          <a href="/agendamento-direto" class="btn-recovery offer-cta">
            Quero Esta Oferta
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="offer-benefits reveal">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Foco em Conversação</h3>
          <p>Aulas 100% em inglês com prática real desde a primeira aula. Você vai falar e ouvir inglês de verdade!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/>
              <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/>
              <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Flexibilidade Total</h3>
          <p>Escolha o horário que melhor se encaixa na sua rotina, qualquer dia da semana</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87"/>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Professores Dedicados</h3>
          <p>Mais de 1.300 professores certificados disponíveis para suas aulas</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .offer-section {
    padding: var(--section-padding) 0;
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.375rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-recovery-cta);
    background: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
  }

  .offer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .offer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }

  /* Offer Card */
  .offer-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-recovery-cta);
  }

  .offer-card-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-recovery-cta) 0%, #15803d 100%);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .offer-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.375rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .offer-price-block {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .currency {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .price {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .period {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .offer-card-body {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Breakdown */
  .offer-breakdown {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .breakdown-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .breakdown-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .breakdown-icon.points {
    background: var(--color-primary-subtle);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .breakdown-icon.tickets {
    background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.15);
    color: #b45309;
  }

  .breakdown-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .breakdown-value {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .breakdown-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
  }

  .breakdown-bonus {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-recovery-cta);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .breakdown-detail {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .breakdown-plus {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
  }

  .breakdown-item.bonus {
    background: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.05);
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px dashed var(--color-recovery-cta);
  }

  /* Total */
  .offer-total {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    padding-top: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .total-line {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .total-label {
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
  }

  .total-value {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .total-line.highlight {
    background: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.1);
    margin: 0 -0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .total-line.highlight .total-value {
    color: var(--color-recovery-cta);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  /* Features */
  .offer-features {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .offer-features li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
  }

  .offer-features li svg {
    color: var(--color-recovery-cta);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .offer-cta {
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* Benefits side */
  .offer-benefits {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .benefit-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .benefit-card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .benefit-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-primary-subtle);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .benefit-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .benefit-card p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
